Comment: 0,0:00:00.01,0:00:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,====================A-PART====================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.11,0:02:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,得快點 把那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.57,0:02:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,給我停下！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.15,0:02:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.88,0:02:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,被那傢伙到達神樹 我們的世界會消失掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.94,0:02:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣就好 一起消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.29,0:02:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,才不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.67,0:02:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,御靈！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.66,0:02:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.55,0:02:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉 也有人一無所知地活著喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.42,0:03:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我們是不能放棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.79,0:03:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,因為那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.56,0:03:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你要說那才是勇者嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,和其他人沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.82,0:03:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,如果沒辦法保護最重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,成為勇者就沒有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.09,0:03:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我提不起勁頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.25,0:03:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈… 你要是就那樣老實待著就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.16,0:03:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,要是睡過去 就一切都解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.49,0:03:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,已經太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,戰鬥不會結束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.70,0:03:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的活地獄沒有盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.63,0:03:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.91,0:03:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.87,0:03:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,因為有東鄉在一起！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.43,0:03:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,無論多麼痛苦 東鄉都由我來保護！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,會忘掉寶貴的心情和回憶喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.27,0:03:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能不要緊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,連友奈和大家的事情也會忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.34,0:04:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒辦法乖乖放棄認命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.78,0:04:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,如果要失去最重要的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.57,0:04:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不會忘記的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.08,0:04:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼能這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.83,0:04:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,無比強烈地這樣想！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.71,0:04:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我們當時…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定也這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.63,0:04:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,現在只記得好悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.05,0:04:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,都不知道自己的淚水有什麼意義！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.57,0:04:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊 我怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.36,0:04:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈肯定也會忘記我的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.54,0:04:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.75,0:05:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不會忘記的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.58,0:05:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不是騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.90,0:05:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.80,0:05:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不是騙人！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.94,0:05:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我會永遠和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.85,0:05:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣一來 就不會忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.74,0:05:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.80,0:05:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不要丟下我一個人～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.91,0:05:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.04,0:05:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.57,0:05:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,太陽…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.64,0:06:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我闖了大禍…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.70,0:06:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不是東鄉的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,要阻止那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.18,0:06:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,給我停下！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.25,0:06:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,停不下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.14,0:06:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對不要放棄…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.29,0:06:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼能在這種地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.66,0:06:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,腿…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.05,0:06:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,已經… 不…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,小樹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 在這麼關鍵的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.61,0:07:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,風前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.26,0:07:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.67,0:07:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來 東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,推回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.03,0:07:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.86,0:07:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,三個人都…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.79,0:07:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那裡嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.95,0:07:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,夏凜！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.62,0:07:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不要小看勇者部！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 勇者部！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我是！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.61,0:08:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,贊州中學勇者部！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.37,0:08:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.28,0:08:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者・結城友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,到達吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.28,0:09:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,結束了… 嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.05,0:09:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.62,0:09:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.81,0:09:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.41,0:09:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:10:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！ 友奈！ 友奈！ 友奈！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.01,0:00:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,====================B-PART====================
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.64,0:10:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的戰鬥不是夢裡的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:16.75,Notice,,0,0,0,,大規模的山火基本被控制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,從實際發生的大規模災害也可以知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.74,0:10:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,起立
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.25,0:10:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,敬禮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.96,0:10:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,向神樹大人 拜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我們所守護 所奪回的日常生活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.13,0:11:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,很快就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.95,0:11:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.80,0:11:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.28,0:11:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,姐… 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.83,0:11:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.96,0:11:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,真的取回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我們會痊癒的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:14.79,Notice,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs37.5}發件人：大赦\N收件人：三好夏凜\N主題　：神諭\N\N敵人的來襲會暫時中止。\N失去精靈的你，也失去了勇者的力量。\N請繼續學生生活。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.94,0:12:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,從那以後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.05,0:12:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,大赦的聯絡一直是單方面的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.33,0:12:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,也沒辦法回信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.64,0:12:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我們是被神樹大人解放了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.70,0:12:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,已經不需要我們了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.29,0:12:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,失去目的了 會不安？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.45,0:12:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.36,0:12:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不許笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.31,0:12:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 外面的世界仍然是那樣沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,希望我們的戰鬥數據能派上用場
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的戰鬥不是無謂的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.99,0:12:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,所以神樹大人才不再尋求祭品了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來只有相信後輩 交給她們了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.70,0:12:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.87,0:12:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 勇者部是不滅的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.57,0:13:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,被你搶先說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.27,0:13:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.58,0:13:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,只有那孩子沒醒來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,因為那孩子… 一個人努力過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.12,0:13:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,犧牲自己不要緊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,這種想法… 我討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.63,0:13:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.92,0:13:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 要不是那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.60,0:13:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.85,0:13:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,今天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.37,0:13:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,風前輩又說了奇怪的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.52,0:13:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.70,0:13:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我們來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.98,0:13:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.64,0:13:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,午安 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.57,0:14:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,這是壓花
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.14,0:14:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.61,0:14:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我… 犧牲了最重要的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.18,0:14:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我做出了那種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不許說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不要說了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.52,0:14:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不是任何人的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.85,0:14:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不是討論過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 距離文化祭已經沒幾天了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.18,0:14:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,關於今後的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.22,0:14:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我想把友奈的角色就那樣保留著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.50,0:14:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.02,0:14:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我的腿都治好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.98,0:14:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈一定也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.72,0:14:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不想那麼冷血
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.65,0:15:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我也沒有那麼冷血啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.98,0:15:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,戲…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.03,0:15:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,戲劇先繼續練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.79,0:15:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,相信友奈她 一定… 一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:25.73,NoticeB,,0,0,0,,{\frz-16\pos(1066,650)}致明日的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.97,0:15:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者無論怎麼受傷 怎麼受傷 都絕不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,因為如果所有人都放棄掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.12,0:15:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這個世界只會陷入黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.96,0:15:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者相信 自己不放棄就能激勵到大家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.69,0:15:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,也有人看不起這樣的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者只是淡淡地一笑了之
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.84,0:15:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,也有人說沒有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.74,0:16:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,儘管如此 勇者也沒有氣餒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,大家接二連三地向魔王屈服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.59,0:16:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不知不覺 勇者只剩孤身一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.58,0:16:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者只剩一個人這件事 沒人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.05,0:16:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,即使只剩一個人 勇者也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者也… 沒有放棄戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.25,0:16:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,因為只要不放棄 希望就不會結束…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.29,0:16:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,無論失去什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.84,0:16:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,就算如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,就算如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.30,0:17:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不想失去最重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.12,0:17:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.32,0:17:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.60,0:17:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,就算再寂寞 再痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是說也要和我一直在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.00,0:17:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,東… 鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.01,0:17:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我都和你在一起 一直
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.75,0:17:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.76,0:18:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉 我都聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.49,0:18:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉的聲音 大家的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.44,0:18:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.48,0:18:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.12,0:18:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,結城友奈 讓大家擔心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.14,0:18:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.32,0:18:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:38.71,Notice,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來 友奈！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.10,0:18:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.43,0:18:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,疼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.15,0:18:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.94,0:18:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,大家沒事太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.21,0:18:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我好擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.96,0:18:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,會不會醒不過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.12,0:18:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我倒是不怎麼擔心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我也以為已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.78,0:19:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.10,0:19:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.60,0:19:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,用韌性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.26,0:19:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,韌性？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.39,0:19:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是神樹大人救了你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.64,0:19:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.91,0:19:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈肯定是憑自己的力量回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.70,0:19:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不是奇跡或神的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.59,0:19:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈是用自己的強烈意志和韌性回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.33,0:19:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.73,0:19:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你等我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.85,0:20:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者相信自己的不屈會激勵大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.46,0:20:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,然後 因為有大家在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,因為相信著大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,所以自己不會輸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,到頭來世上都是討厭的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.88,0:20:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,都是痛苦的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.05,0:20:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你也裝作沒看見 墮落吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.17,0:20:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.06,0:20:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不要抵抗了 被冰冷的現實凍僵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.84,0:20:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那種事是心情決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.88,0:20:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.95,0:20:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,只要重視對方就能成為朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.06,0:20:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,只要心心相印 就能變強無數倍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.85,0:20:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,韌性會無限地湧出來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.63,0:20:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然世上有很多討厭的事情 悲傷的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:21:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,自己無可奈何的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.49,0:21:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,但只要有最喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.65,0:21:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,就不可能氣餒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.65,0:21:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.77,0:21:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,因為有最喜歡的人在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.19,0:21:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,無論多少次都能站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.64,0:21:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.30,0:21:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者絕對不會輸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.06,0:21:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.28,0:21:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.81,0:21:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.23,0:21:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.83,0:21:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.10,0:21:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.88,0:22:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,頭有點暈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.26,0:22:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.24,0:22:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.14,0:22:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼困難都能克服
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.22,0:22:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,和最喜歡的大家一起的話
